page.title: 20Employment in Painswick
page.content:
Most of the jobs in our block are farming.Other work found here is either Solicitors,Dentists,Shops, Hotels or restaurants. In Painswick all jobs have been taken and there are no vacancies.We found out that the employment situation is very good for a rural area.
